--- infra [shared,critical] ---
DB        [R#*]  : PostgreSQL | AllRepos → THIS
Cache     [R#*]  : Valkey cache layer | Sers → THIS
Err       [U*]   : typed error classes | AllSers ← THIS
EvtBus    [U*~]  : domain event bus | AllSers ↔ THIS
---

--- middleware [shared] ---
MidAuth   [M*$]  : JWT validate, attach user+perms | AllConts → THIS
MidTen    [M*$]  : Extract tenant_id, set RLS var | AllConts → THIS → MidAuth
MidErr    [M*]   : Catch typed errors, return JSON | App → THIS → Err
---
